description:
Watch the Goku (Mini) Trailer for Dragon Ball: Sparking Zero, an upcoming 3D anime action fighter developed by Spike Chunsoft Co. Ltd. Players will return to the legendary gameplay of the Budokai Tenkaichi series as fighters go head-to-head. Take a look at the trailer to get a glimpse of Goku (Mini)'s Ultimate Attack: Power Pole Rush. Dragon Ball: Sparking Zero is launching on October 11 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).

description: The Silent Hill 2 Remake, by Bloober Team, is the most miserable experience I've had with a game, and that's why this 2024 remake is great. Whether it's the suffocating fog, or the unrelenting darkness of Silent Hill 2's many deadly corridors, Silent Hill 2's nightmarish vision has been preserved, and meaningfully altered for the modern era. This retelling of 2001's Silent Hill 2 is available on PS5 (PlayStation 5) and PC via Steam on October 8, 2024.
title: Silent Hill 2 Is Utterly Miserable (And That's Why It's Great)
